WEBVTT

00:00.000 --> 00:10.640
Dear Tony, I go to a new school in Cambridge now. I like it very much. I'm making a lot of

00:10.640 --> 00:21.960
new friends. I'm studying new subjects like science. It's very interesting. We're using

00:21.960 --> 00:31.440
computers and learning how to use the internet. We write emails to people in different countries.

00:31.440 --> 00:44.360
I'm learning how people live in different countries. It's great. We do PE on Wednesday in the afternoon.

00:44.360 --> 00:55.520
Sometimes we stay in the sports hall to do sports and I like that too. I play football after

00:55.520 --> 01:06.720
school on Mondays. I like playing football a lot. I'm enjoying my new school. Write and tell me

01:06.720 --> 01:11.320
what you're doing in your school in China. John.

